This sketch demonstrates some possible
interactions that enable us to observe
and discover other visual effects :
( we've added some randomness )

- KEY 'r' regenerates a new random sequence
- KEYS '+' & '-' increase/decrease size of circles
- KEYS 'UP' & 'DOWN' increase/decrease y interval
- KEYS 'RIGHT' & 'LEFT' increase/decrease x interval   
- KEYS 'w' & 'x' increase/decrease contour thickness
- KEYS 'a' & 'z' increase/decrease length of lines of cross


